{"title":"Linux文件管理与查询","uid":"7e1e754a6541fda39aaf072fd6373097","slug":"Linux文件管理与查询","date":"2025-07-30T02:11:06.000Z","updated":"2025-07-31T07:33:41.774Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Linux文件管理与查询.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Linux文件管理与查询\"><a href=\"#Linux文件管理与查询\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Linux文件管理与查询\"></a>Linux文件管理与查询</h1><h2 id=\"一、grep命令\"><a href=\"#一、grep命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、grep命令\"></a>一、grep命令</h2><h3 id=\"基础语法\"><a href=\"#基础语法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础语法\"></a>基础语法</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep [选项] <span class=\"string\">&quot;搜索模式&quot;</span> 文件或目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"常用选项\"><a href=\"#常用选项\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用选项\"></a>常用选项</h4><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730102755322.png\" alt=\"image-20250730102755322\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"正则表达式\"><a href=\"#正则表达式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"正则表达式\"></a>正则表达式</h3><h4 id=\"1-基础语法\"><a href=\"#1-基础语法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 基础语法\"></a>1. 基础语法</h4><ul>\n<li><p><strong><code>.</code></strong> (点)：匹配任意单个字符</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;a.c&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;abc&quot;, &quot;aac&quot;, &quot;a1c&quot; 等</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>*</code></strong>：匹配前一个字符0次或多次</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;ab*c&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;ac&quot;, &quot;abc&quot;, &quot;abbc&quot; 等</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>[]</code></strong>：匹配括号内的任意字符</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;[aeiou]&quot;</span> file.txt   <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配任意元音字母</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;[0-9]&quot;</span> file.txt     <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配任意数字</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>[^]</code></strong>：匹配不属于括号内指定字符集的单个字符</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;[^0-9]&quot;</span> file.txt     <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配非数字字符</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"2-位置锚定\"><a href=\"#2-位置锚定\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2. 位置锚定\"></a>2. 位置锚定</h4><ul>\n<li><p><strong><code>^</code></strong>：匹配行首</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;^start&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配以 &quot;start&quot; 开头的行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>$</code></strong>：匹配行尾</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;end$&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配以 &quot;end&quot; 结尾的行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"3-扩展正则表达式（需-E）\"><a href=\"#3-扩展正则表达式（需-E）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3. 扩展正则表达式（需 -E）\"></a>3. 扩展正则表达式（需 <code>-E</code>）</h4><p>使用 <code>grep -E</code> 或 <code>egrep</code> 启用高级语法：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><strong><code>+</code></strong>：匹配前一个字符至少1次</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -E <span class=\"string\">&quot;a+&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;a&quot;, &quot;aa&quot;（等价于 aa*）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>?</code></strong>：匹配前一个字符0或1次</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -E <span class=\"string\">&quot;colou?r&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;color&quot; 或 &quot;colour&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>|</code></strong>：或匹配</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -E <span class=\"string\">&quot;cat|dog&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;cat&quot; 或 &quot;dog&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>()</code></strong>：分组</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -E <span class=\"string\">&quot;(abc)&#123;2&#125;&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;abcabc&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p><strong><code>&#123;&#125;</code></strong>：用于 精确控制前一个字符&#x2F;模式的重复次数</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>&#123;n&#125;</code>：精确重复 n 次</li>\n<li><code>&#123;n,&#125;</code>：重复至少 n 次</li>\n<li><code>&#123;n,m&#125;</code>：重复 n 到 m 次</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -E <span class=\"string\">&quot;go&#123;3,5&#125;gle&quot;</span> file.txt  <span class=\"comment\"># 匹配 &quot;gooogle&quot; 和 &quot;goooogle&quot;，但不匹配 &quot;google&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n</ul>\n<p>使用 <code>grep</code> 时，可以通过 <strong>正则表达式（Regular Expressions）</strong> 实现高效文本匹配。以下是常见用法和示例：</p>\n<h4 id=\"4-字符类\"><a href=\"#4-字符类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4. 字符类\"></a>4. 字符类</h4><ul>\n<li><strong><code>\\w</code></strong>：字母、数字、下划线（等价于 <code>[a-zA-Z0-9_]</code>）</li>\n<li><strong><code>\\d</code></strong>：数字（等价于 <code>[0-9]</code>）</li>\n<li><strong><code>\\s</code></strong>：空白字符（空格、制表符等）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"实验练习准备：\"><a href=\"#实验练习准备：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验练习准备：\"></a>实验练习准备：</h3><p>创建practice.txt文件，在桌面上打开终端</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim practice.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>在vim编辑器里将下面内容复制进去，保存后退出，在桌面上得到一个practice.txt文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730103127763.png\" alt=\"image-20250730103127763\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"实验练习：\"><a href=\"#实验练习：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验练习：\"></a>实验练习：</h3><h4 id=\"实验-1-1：查找错误日志\"><a href=\"#实验-1-1：查找错误日志\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 1.1：查找错误日志\"></a>实验 1.1：查找错误日志</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> practice.txt                <span class=\"comment\">#输出所有包含 &quot;ERROR&quot; 的行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730103900075.png\" alt=\"image-20250730103900075\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-1-2：忽略大小写匹配\"><a href=\"#实验-1-2：忽略大小写匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 1.2：忽略大小写匹配\"></a>实验 1.2：忽略大小写匹配</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -i <span class=\"string\">&quot;error&quot;</span> practice.txt             <span class=\"comment\">#匹配 &quot;error&quot;（不区分大小写）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep -i <span class=\"string\">&quot;warning&quot;</span> practice.txt           <span class=\"comment\">#匹配 &quot;WARNING&quot;（不区分大小写）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730104233186.png\" alt=\"image-20250730104233186\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-1-3：反向排除调试信息\"><a href=\"#实验-1-3：反向排除调试信息\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 1.3：反向排除调试信息\"></a>实验 1.3：反向排除调试信息</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -v <span class=\"string\">&quot;WARNING&quot;</span> practice.txt            <span class=\"comment\">#排除包含 &quot;WARNING&quot; 的行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730104443521.png\" alt=\"image-20250730104443521\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-2-1：显示匹配行号\"><a href=\"#实验-2-1：显示匹配行号\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 2.1：显示匹配行号\"></a>实验 2.1：显示匹配行号</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -n <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> practice.txt              <span class=\"comment\">#输出行号，如 `2:...[ERROR]...`</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730110948711.png\" alt=\"image-20250730110948711\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-2-2：统计错误次数\"><a href=\"#实验-2-2：统计错误次数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 2.2：统计错误次数\"></a>实验 2.2：统计错误次数</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -c <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> practice.txt              <span class=\"comment\">#输出错误行数（示例结果：3）</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730111115111.png\" alt=\"image-20250730111115111\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-3-1：查看错误上下文\"><a href=\"#实验-3-1：查看错误上下文\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 3.1：查看错误上下文\"></a>实验 3.1：查看错误上下文</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -C 1 <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> practice.txt            <span class=\"comment\">#显示每个 &quot;ERROR&quot; 行及其前后各 1 行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep -C 2 <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> practice.txt            <span class=\"comment\">#显示每个 &quot;ERROR&quot; 行及其前后各 2 行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730111301346.png\" alt=\"image-20250730111301346\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730111326569.png\" alt=\"image-20250730111326569\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-4-1：匹配时间范围\"><a href=\"#实验-4-1：匹配时间范围\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 4.1：匹配时间范围\"></a>实验 4.1：匹配时间范围</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;2023-10-01 08:1.&quot;</span> practice.txt          <span class=\"comment\">#匹配 08:10 以后的行</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&quot;^2023-10-01 08:1&quot;</span> practice.txt          <span class=\"comment\">#匹配行首为2023-10-01 08:1 的行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730111528323.png\" alt=\"image-20250730111528323\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730111708979.png\" alt=\"image-20250730111708979\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-4-2：提取-IP-地址\"><a href=\"#实验-4-2：提取-IP-地址\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 4.2：提取 IP 地址\"></a>实验 4.2：提取 IP 地址</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -Eo <span class=\"string\">&quot;([0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;\\.)&#123;3&#125;[0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;&quot;</span> practice.txt    <span class=\"comment\">#输出所有 IP 地址，如 192.168.1.100</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730104730132.png\" alt=\"image-20250730104730132\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -E <span class=\"string\">&quot;([0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;\\.)&#123;3&#125;[0-9]&#123;1,3&#125;&quot;</span> practice.txt     <span class=\"comment\">#输出含有 IP 地址的行，如 192.168.1.100</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730104905802.png\" alt=\"image-20250730104905802\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-4-3：精确匹配警告\"><a href=\"#实验-4-3：精确匹配警告\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 4.3：精确匹配警告\"></a>实验 4.3：精确匹配警告</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -w <span class=\"string\">&quot;WARNING&quot;</span> practice.txt             <span class=\"comment\">#精确匹配&quot;WARNING&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730111814626.png\" alt=\"image-20250730111814626\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-5-1：提取邮箱地址\"><a href=\"#实验-5-1：提取邮箱地址\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 5.1：提取邮箱地址\"></a>实验 5.1：提取邮箱地址</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep -Eio <span class=\"string\">&quot;\\b[A-Za-z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Za-z0-9.-]+\\.[A-Z]&#123;2,&#125;\\b&quot;</span> practice.txt     <span class=\"comment\">#输出邮箱地址</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep -Eio <span class=\"string\">&quot;\\b[A-Z0-9._%+-]+@[A-Z0-9.-]+\\.[A-Z]&#123;2,&#125;\\b&quot;</span> practice.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730105543430.png\" alt=\"image-20250730105543430\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-5-2：查找金额记录\"><a href=\"#实验-5-2：查找金额记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 5.2：查找金额记录\"></a>实验 5.2：查找金额记录</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"string\">&#x27;\\$&#x27;</span> practice.txt</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730112427816.png\" alt=\"image-20250730112427816\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-6-1：扩展练习（目录递归）\"><a href=\"#实验-6-1：扩展练习（目录递归）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 6.1：扩展练习（目录递归）\"></a>实验 6.1：扩展练习（目录递归）</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 创建目录结构</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> -p /tmp/practice/logs/</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">cp</span> practice.txt /tmp/practice/logs/</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">echo</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR: File not found&quot;</span> &gt; /tmp/practice/error.log</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730110457989.png\" alt=\"image-20250730110457989\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 递归搜索所有 &quot;ERROR&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep -r <span class=\"string\">&quot;ERROR&quot;</span> /tmp/practice/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730110636945.png\" alt=\"image-20250730110636945\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 排除 .log 文件 --exclude=&quot;*.log&quot; 排除所有 .log </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep -r --exclude=<span class=\"string\">&quot;*.log&quot;</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;INFO&quot;</span> /tmp/practice/</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730110803437.png\" alt=\"image-20250730110803437\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"二、find命令\"><a href=\"#二、find命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、find命令\"></a>二、find命令</h2><h3 id=\"基础语法-1\"><a href=\"#基础语法-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"基础语法\"></a>基础语法</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find [搜索路径] [匹配条件] [执行动作]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"常用匹配条件\"><a href=\"#常用匹配条件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用匹配条件\"></a>常用匹配条件</h4><h5 id=\"按名称或路径匹配\"><a href=\"#按名称或路径匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"按名称或路径匹配\"></a>按名称或路径匹配</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155526689.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155526689\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"按文件类型匹配\"><a href=\"#按文件类型匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"按文件类型匹配\"></a>按文件类型匹配</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155549562.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155549562\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"按文件大小匹配\"><a href=\"#按文件大小匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"按文件大小匹配\"></a>按文件大小匹配</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155613690.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155613690\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"按时间戳匹配\"><a href=\"#按时间戳匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"按时间戳匹配\"></a>按时间戳匹配</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155635808.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155635808\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"按权限匹配\"><a href=\"#按权限匹配\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"按权限匹配\"></a>按权限匹配</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155701438.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155701438\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"逻辑操作符\"><a href=\"#逻辑操作符\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"逻辑操作符\"></a>逻辑操作符</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155732693.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155732693\"></p>\n<h5 id=\"执行动作\"><a href=\"#执行动作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"执行动作\"></a>执行动作</h5><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730155754759.png\" alt=\"image-20250730155754759\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"实验练习准备\"><a href=\"#实验练习准备\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验练习准备\"></a>实验练习准备</h3><p>创建练习目录结构</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> -p ~/find-practice/&#123;logs,data,backup&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">touch</span> ~/find-practice/logs/&#123;app.log,error.log&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">touch</span> ~/find-practice/data/&#123;file1.txt,file2.csv,image.jpg&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">mkdir</span> ~/find-practice/backup/old</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">touch</span> ~/find-practice/backup/old/archive.tar.gz</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"实验练习\"><a href=\"#实验练习\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验练习\"></a>实验练习</h3><h4 id=\"实验-1-1：按名称搜索文件\"><a href=\"#实验-1-1：按名称搜索文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 1.1：按名称搜索文件\"></a>实验 1.1：按名称搜索文件</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice/ -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*.log&quot;</span>            <span class=\"comment\">#输出所有 .log 文件的路径</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730161233333.png\" alt=\"image-20250730161233333\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-1-2：按类型搜索目录\"><a href=\"#实验-1-2：按类型搜索目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 1.2：按类型搜索目录\"></a>实验 1.2：按类型搜索目录</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -<span class=\"built_in\">type</span> d                   <span class=\"comment\">#列出所有子目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730161107220.png\" alt=\"image-20250730161107220\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-1-3：组合条件（名称与大小）\"><a href=\"#实验-1-3：组合条件（名称与大小）\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 1.3：组合条件（名称与大小）\"></a>实验 1.3：组合条件（名称与大小）</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*.jpg&quot;</span> -size -10k  <span class=\"comment\">#查找小于 10KB 的 .jpg 文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730161545249.png\" alt=\"image-20250730161545249\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-2-1：查找最近修改的文件\"><a href=\"#实验-2-1：查找最近修改的文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 2.1：查找最近修改的文件\"></a>实验 2.1：查找最近修改的文件</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -mtime -1          <span class=\"comment\"># 列出 1 天内修改过的文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730161730780.png\" alt=\"image-20250730161730780\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-2-2：排除特定权限文件\"><a href=\"#实验-2-2：排除特定权限文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 2.2：排除特定权限文件\"></a>实验 2.2：排除特定权限文件</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice ! -perm 644     <span class=\"comment\"># 查找权限不是 644 的文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730161919139.png\" alt=\"image-20250730161919139\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">需求</th>\n<th align=\"center\">权限</th>\n<th align=\"center\">字母表示</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\">私有文件</td>\n<td align=\"center\">600</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-rw-------</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">标准共享</td>\n<td align=\"center\">644</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-rw-r--r--</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">组内共享</td>\n<td align=\"center\">664</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-rw-rw-r--</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">可执行文件</td>\n<td align=\"center\">755</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-rwxr-xr-x</code></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\">共享目录</td>\n<td align=\"center\">775</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>drwxrwxr-x</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h4 id=\"实验-3-1：删除空文件\"><a href=\"#实验-3-1：删除空文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 3.1：删除空文件\"></a>实验 3.1：删除空文件</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -size 0 -delete     <span class=\"comment\"># 删除所有空文件</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730162706405.png\" alt=\"image-20250730162706405\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-3-2：批量修改权限\"><a href=\"#实验-3-2：批量修改权限\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 3.2：批量修改权限\"></a>实验 3.2：批量修改权限</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*.sh&quot;</span> -<span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> &#123;&#125; <span class=\"built_in\">chmod</span> &#123;&#125; 755 \\;             <span class=\"comment\"># 将所有 .sh 文件设为可执行</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h4 id=\"实验-3-3：搜索并压缩文件\"><a href=\"#实验-3-3：搜索并压缩文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 3.3：搜索并压缩文件\"></a>实验 3.3：搜索并压缩文件</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">touch</span> ~/find-practice/logs/&#123;app.log,error.log&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*.log&quot;</span> -<span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> tar -cvsf logs.tar.gz &#123;&#125; +   <span class=\"comment\"># 将 .log 文件打包为 logs.tar.gz</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730164006305.png\" alt=\"image-20250730164006305\"></p>\n<p>tar命令</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">选项</th>\n<th align=\"center\">作用</th>\n<th align=\"center\">常见用法</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-c</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">创建新归档文件</td>\n<td align=\"center\">必选（创建模式）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-v</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">显示详细过程（verbose）</td>\n<td align=\"center\">可选（显示打包文件列表）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-s</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><em>已废弃</em> 原始排序（obsolete sort）</td>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong>现代 tar 已忽略此选项</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><code>-f</code></td>\n<td align=\"center\">指定归档文件名</td>\n<td align=\"center\">必选（后接文件名）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h4 id=\"实验-4-1：忽略特定目录\"><a href=\"#实验-4-1：忽略特定目录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 4.1：忽略特定目录\"></a>实验 4.1：忽略特定目录</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -path <span class=\"string\">&quot;*/backup&quot;</span> -prune -o -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*.txt&quot;</span> -<span class=\"built_in\">print</span>  <span class=\"comment\"># 查找所有 .txt 文件，但跳过 backup 目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>提前创建了一个111.txt</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730164624143.png\" alt=\"image-20250730164624143\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"实验-4-2：结合-xargs-处理文件\"><a href=\"#实验-4-2：结合-xargs-处理文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实验 4.2：结合  xargs 处理文件\"></a>实验 4.2：结合  xargs 处理文件</h4><p><code>xargs</code> 是 Linux&#x2F;Unix 系统中一个极其强大的命令行工具，用于<strong>构建和执行命令行参数</strong>。它弥补了管道(<code>|</code>)只能传递标准输出的不足，将输入数据转换为命令参数。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">[命令产生输入] | xargs [选项] [目标命令]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"center\">选项</th>\n<th align=\"center\">作用</th>\n<th align=\"center\">示例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-I &#123;&#125;</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">自定义占位符</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;ls</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-n N</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">每组N个参数</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;seq 10</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-P N</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">并发进程数</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;find .</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-t</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">打印执行命令</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;echo “f”</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-p</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">交互式确认</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;ls</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-0</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">处理特殊字符</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;find -print0</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><strong><code>-d</code></strong></td>\n<td align=\"center\">自定义分隔符</td>\n<td align=\"center\">&#96;echo “a,b,c”</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find ~/find-practice -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*.csv&quot;</span> | xargs -I &#123;&#125; <span class=\"built_in\">mv</span> &#123;&#125; ~/find-practice/data    <span class=\"comment\">#移动所有 .csv 文件到 data 目录</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"常用场景\"><a href=\"#常用场景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"常用场景\"></a>常用场景</h3><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730184939937.png\" alt=\"image-20250730184939937\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"案例学习\"><a href=\"#案例学习\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"案例学习\"></a>案例学习</h3><h4 id=\"1、找出系统中名为-passwd的文件\"><a href=\"#1、找出系统中名为-passwd的文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、找出系统中名为 passwd的文件\"></a>1、找出系统中名为 passwd的文件</h4><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find / -name passwd -<span class=\"built_in\">type</span> f</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730190153801.png\" alt=\"image-20250730190153801\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"2、找出-tmp目录中文件名带nz的文件，然后删除\"><a href=\"#2、找出-tmp目录中文件名带nz的文件，然后删除\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、找出&#x2F;tmp目录中文件名带nz的文件，然后删除\"></a>2、找出&#x2F;tmp目录中文件名带nz的文件，然后删除</h4><p>由于&#x2F;tmp目录下没有带nz的文件，所以先创建几个文件</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730185424868.png\" alt=\"image-20250730185424868\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">find /tmp -name <span class=\"string\">&quot;*nz*&quot;</span> -<span class=\"built_in\">type</span> f -<span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> <span class=\"built_in\">rm</span> -fr <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#123;&#125;&#x27;</span> \\;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/Five0ne15/picgo_pic@main/picgo_picture/image-20250730185948107.png\" alt=\"image-20250730185948107\"></p>\n","text":"Linux文件管理与查询一、grep命令基础语法1grep [选项] \"搜索模式\" 文件或目录 常用选项 正则表达式1. 基础语法 . (点)：匹配任意单个字符...","permalink":"/post/Linux文件管理与查询","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"5.7k","symbolsTime":"5 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"Linux","slug":"Linux","count":9,"path":"api/tags/Linux.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Linux%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%9F%A5%E8%AF%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Linux文件管理与查询</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E3%80%81grep%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一、grep命令</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">基础语法</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E9%80%89%E9%A1%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">常用选项</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%AD%A3%E5%88%99%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F\"><span class=\"toc-text\">正则表达式</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#1-%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">1. 基础语法</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2-%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E9%94%9A%E5%AE%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2. 位置锚定</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#3-%E6%89%A9%E5%B1%95%E6%AD%A3%E5%88%99%E8%A1%A8%E8%BE%BE%E5%BC%8F%EF%BC%88%E9%9C%80-E%EF%BC%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">3. 扩展正则表达式（需 -E）</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#4-%E5%AD%97%E7%AC%A6%E7%B1%BB\"><span class=\"toc-text\">4. 字符类</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验练习准备：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验练习：</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C-1-1%EF%BC%9A%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%BE%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验 1.1：查找错误日志</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C-1-2%EF%BC%9A%E5%BF%BD%E7%95%A5%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%8F%E5%86%99%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验 1.2：忽略大小写匹配</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C-1-3%EF%BC%9A%E5%8F%8D%E5%90%91%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E8%B0%83%E8%AF%95%E4%BF%A1%E6%81%AF\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验 1.3：反向排除调试信息</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C-2-1%EF%BC%9A%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E5%8C%B9%E9%85%8D%E8%A1%8C%E5%8F%B7\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验 2.1：显示匹配行号</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C-2-2%EF%BC%9A%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%A1%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E6%AC%A1%E6%95%B0\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验 2.2：统计错误次数</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9E%E9%AA%8C-3-1%EF%BC%9A%E6%9F%A5%E7%9C%8B%E9%94%99%E8%AF%AF%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%8B%E6%96%87\"><span class=\"toc-text\">实验 3.1：查看错误上下文</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"